  },
  {
    "time": "00:02:31",
    "en": "And here are my instruments.",
    "zh": "這是我的工具。",
    "ja": "こちらが私の器具です。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:02:34",
    "en": "All right.",
    "zh": "好的。",
    "ja": "よし。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:02:35",
    "en": "Let's start with your front teeth.",
    "zh": "我們先從你的門牙開始。",
