    "ja": "使っていますか？"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:04",
    "en": "Mm-hmm.",
    "zh": "嗯嗯。",
    "ja": "うん。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:05",
    "en": "I try.",
    "zh": "我有試著用。",
    "ja": "使おうとしています。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:06",
    "en": "Good girl.",
    "zh": "乖孩子。",
    "ja": "いい子ですね。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:07",
    "en": "It's important to try to do that every day to keep them very clean.",
