    "ja": "彼が必要です。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:32",
    "en": "Mr. Slurpy.",
    "zh": "吸水器先生。",
    "ja": "スラーピーさん。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:33",
    "en": "Yes.",
    "zh": "是的。",
    "ja": "はい。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:03:34",
    "en": "Because they're saliva in your mouth.",
